57
00:02:50.431 --> 00:02:51.519
I'm it!

58
00:02:51.693 --> 00:02:53.260
I choose the asset.

59
00:02:53.390 --> 00:02:55.436
I choose the cover.
I build the fucking plan.

60
00:02:55.523 --> 00:02:56.828
