247
00:12:52.249 --> 00:12:54.425
<i>♪</i>

248
00:13:12.835 --> 00:13:15.838
It's fine. It's fine.

249
00:13:18.232 --> 00:13:20.016
I told you
to stop playing rugby.

250
00:13:20.147 --> 00:13:21.975
